{"tid":305331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲嘅兄弟姊妹會帶條仔/女返屋企訓？","createTime":"2017-07-01T14:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T00:06:16.000Z","uid":78053,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d32b91a1f78c39f01446da9f9e96831cd9e287c0","tid":305331,"uid":78053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"我哥成日帶條女返屋企 <br />\n有時甚至會過夜<br />\n經常聽到佢地啲扑野聲 平時又好撚嘈<br />\n我真係頂唔順 鬧極都要帶條女返屋企<br />\n成家無一個中意佢呢個行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉除左搬出去根本無辨法可以脫離佢地<br />\n點解呢個世上會有人咁唔知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 絲<br />\n仲要同我哥同一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d24cda09d0302fba22af7c3a91a33a11987a93","tid":305331,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dc352aefb5ab1db3d6673b1595030577bfe48f9","tid":305331,"uid":78053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你爸爸媽媽唔可以叫佢以後唔準帶返黎咩??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母係會做門面功夫嘅人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對啲外人鬼咁好<br />\n其實我老母屌過佢架 佢都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4c8fe45a944d6bad29f39d34843fa78052f2f6","tid":305331,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"Sorry囉<br />\n無錢開房呀嘛"},{"pid":"d92761606301c5d60ea55519ae0fb259a44fe463","tid":305331,"uid":78053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sorry囉<br />\n無錢開房呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去後樓梯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj