/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為扑野大哂囉，第日到你帶仔上去"},{"pid":"2f158ba942f7b8b4883fda3bf08a0270001bfec8","tid":305331,"uid":103212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ef32006dbb85f916d2e4774a6b742076acddd14","tid":305331,"uid":78053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又帶 制衡下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有時嬲嬲地都真係幾想帶下男朋友返去嘈下佢<br />\n但我知醜架 無佢地咁撚無恥<br />\n人厚臉皮天下無敵啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4349ec93ce5841218a0392a2116094d1307b1a8f","tid":305331,"uid":78053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你夠膽既話 下次佢地扑野個陣條女嗌<br />\n<br />\n妳就發佢圍 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n                  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母我想訓呀 快撚D 射啦爆個臭系啦呀哥</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腦入面成日都ff咁講<br />\n但又唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者試下佢地嘈到你個陣 你突然 唉！一聲 每次都用呢個方法<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定無引</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過特登整啲聲出黎 但佢地好似無咩反應<br />\n可能情到濃時都係咩都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5423b592e28f460a1c64e7e1bf4014d1d7f65a81","tid":305331,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bd0431214756e4c0987cd95329d1b69540e8eb7","tid":305331,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sorry囉<br />\n無錢開房呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去後樓梯囉<img src=\"/a